paint.shared.objects

Class Square

  • java.lang.Object
    • paint.shared.objects.Square

  • public class Square
extends Object
    Represents a rectangular region (square) within a recording or experiment, with its coordinates, statistics, and related tracks.

        Creates a Square with explicit coordinates and identifiers.

        uniqueKey - unique identifier
        experimentName - experiment name
        recordingName - recording name
        squareNumber - sequential number
        rowNumber - row index in grid

        y0 - top coordinate in pixels
        x1 - right coordinate in pixels
        y1 - bottom coordinate in pixels
